<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2025—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/119/4">Pub. L. 119–4</ref> substituted “<date date="2025-09-30">September 30, 2025</date>” for “<date date="2025-03-14">March 14, 2025</date>”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2024—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/118/158">Pub. L. 118–158</ref> substituted “<date date="2025-03-14">March 14, 2025</date>” for “<date date="2024-12-20">December 20, 2024</date>”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/118/83">Pub. L. 118–83</ref> substituted “<date date="2024-12-20">December 20, 2024</date>” for “<date date="2024-09-30">September 30, 2024</date>”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/118/47">Pub. L. 118–47</ref> substituted “<date date="2024-09-30">September 30, 2024</date>” for “<date date="2023-09-30">September 30, 2023</date>”.</p>
