<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2018—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/115/278/s2/h/1/G/i">Pub. L. 115–278, § 2(h)(1)(G)(i)</ref>, substituted “<ref href="/us/usc/t6/s663">section 663 of this title</ref>” for “<ref href="/us/usc/t6/s151">section 151 of this title</ref>, as added by section 223(a)(6) of this division,”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/115/278/s2/h/1/G/ii">Pub. L. 115–278, § 2(h)(1)(G)(ii)</ref>, substituted “<ref href="/us/usc/t6/s663/d/2">section 663(d)(2) of this title</ref>” for “<ref href="/us/usc/t6/s151/d/2">section 151(d)(2) of this title</ref>, as added by section 223(a)(6) of this division,”.</p>
</note>
